data.description: Look no further... This Beautiful two story, 3-bed, 2.5-bath, is conveniently located in the gated community of Fairway Pointe. This peaceful sanctuary lies on the border of the city of Margate and Coral Springs. This home consists of high ceilings, with an open floorplan. The kitchen is spacious with a centered island. It hosts a front living room, dining area, and additional space. The master bedroom is located on the first floor with its own bathroom.  The shower and bathtub are separate. Two additional bedrooms are located upstairs with an option to convert the loft into a 4th bedroom. The home features modern appliances and hosts a two car garage. Contact us today to schedule your tour.
